üö® Add a Timeout for all System Default Shells. This example is for Bash, my chosen language.
vi /etc/profile
Add in these following Lines:
HOSTNAME= `/bin/hostname`
HISTSIZE=1000
TMOUT=7200
We also Have to add the TMOOUT to our path and source 

